dataList.title: Gang Tingtang
dataList.content: Capo! Alcuni fagioli che non ci hanno detto da dove vengono sono entrati in città all'improvviso!

dataList.title: Gang Tingtang
dataList.content: Chi vi ha mandati? Il modo in cui vestite mi dice che non siete né Los Habaneros né Butchers…

dataList.title: Gang Tingtang
dataList.content: Vi darò la possibilità di prostarvi per essere perdonati. Fatelo e vi lascerò andare con gli arti intatti.
…We should gladly part if you were to take off your clothing for us.
That makes it sound kinda weird.

dataList.title: Gang Tingtang
dataList.content: Boss… I think they might be the… odd pods people have been talking about… y'know, rumored to fadangle with people's odors.

dataList.title: Gang Tingtang
dataList.content: Greh… Disgusting bunch… Lemme tell ya, that's no way to live…
Now, our assumed big boss of the gang is looking at us with genuine disgust.
<…I have not wanted to win a fight as desperately as I do now.>
